This product is a clean-room implementation. It implements the ODBC
interface specification (a published Microsoft standard) and speaks the
Oracle TNS/TTC wire protocol, which is reverse-engineered from public
references and the project's own packet captures. It contains no Oracle
source code and no code copied from any other ODBC driver. See
CONTRIBUTING.md for the clean-room development rules.

